### TL;DR

v0.1.41 Founder install on M1: Phase 1 + Phase 2 (gemma4:12b download with granular UI) both CLEAN. Phase 3 "STEP 3 OF 3: SETTING UP FULL TIER... / Finalizing your setup..." → **stuck >10 minutes** — spinner-only, never transitions to onboarding-complete. Dispatch 4 parallel Sonnet 4.6 SEGs to probe root cause (Ollama state, renderer transition logic, IPC emit pattern, CDP runtime probe), then fix + ship v0.1.42.

---

### Why this matters

Phase 3 is the last mile before the user sees MnemosyneC's AI. A stuck spinner with no forward progress at "Finalizing your setup..." is a silent failure — no feedback, no escape, no completion. Violates `canon_long_running_progress_heartbeat_canon_bp078` (>5 min with no state change = broken) and `feedback_every_click_visible_feedback_canon_bp078` (no visible transition). Founder observed this on a live M1 install 2026-06-10 ~18:30 local. Blocking the launch-walk.

